Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.20,0:00:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流动的水没有形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.92,0:00:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂流的风找不到踪迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.72,0:00:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何案件的推理都取决于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.67,0:00:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家一起换个方式看问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该有的却没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.05,0:00:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表看似是小孩 头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字就是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.97,0:01:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回响在黑暗之中的神秘枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.05,0:01:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周一晚上的侦探剧场有不少英俊的男演员出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.35,0:01:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会说点什么呢 真有点紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够呛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.07,0:02:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当事人是电视剧公司的社长也不能就联想到那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.97,0:02:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的工作是给她妈妈做贴身警卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个人3天前被人袭击受了点伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.37,0:02:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经营融资公司竟然是这么危险的行业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.01,0:02:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她逼人还债的手段太狠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以仇家就很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 就是这么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.37,0:02:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.98,0:02:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和古川悦子预约了7点钟见面的侦探毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.82,0:02:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 确实预约了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.62,0:02:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门已经打开了 请进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.03,0:02:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.12,0:02:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.46,0:02:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.57,0:03:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.83,0:03:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悦子小姐对时间要求得很严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.33,0:03:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.13,0:03:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.13,0:03:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.24,0:03:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 等的时候能不能看看电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.50,0:03:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.77,0:03:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个电视机今天早上出了点毛病 看不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.87,0:03:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.88,0:03:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.91,0:03:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么事情这么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.64,0:03:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 靠路边的2楼上最左边的窗户开着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那间是这房子的女主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.34,0:03:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川金融的社长古川和江的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了 请问你是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川浩二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个女社长的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.27,0:03:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是在这个时间开窗换气的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.99,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.29,0:03:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.37,0:03:59.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是姐姐雇来的侦探吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.13,0:04:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人利用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.31,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被人利用吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 肯定是悦子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.53,0:04:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 悦子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.74,0:04:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来晚了 快开门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 马上就开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公司耽误了一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.92,0:04:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.27,0:04:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 好久不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.97,0:04:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一阵妈妈不是和你说不让你进这个门了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.58,0:04:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦 这是我的家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 你的表怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.77,0:04:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子表 便宜货 装什么蒜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.34,0:04:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你的瑞士表被借钱的人抢走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.92,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二 你是不是又来让妈妈替你还帐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.98,0:05:04.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.18,0:05:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也雇了侦探来讨好妈妈吗 我看得很清楚耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.17,0:05:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.36,0:05:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 悦子小姐的公司就快破产了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.55,0:05:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二先生嗜赌 被暴力团逼着还钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是需要钱的话 她妈妈和江女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.27,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 她认为没有希望的公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是亲生孩子也不会借钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.87,0:05:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 以前好像总是给浩二先生钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.72,0:05:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 他要的实在太多了 最后就不让他进门了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.56,0:05:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.75,0:05:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我去叫妈妈起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.24,0:05:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该在自己房间里睡觉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.26,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别光听姐姐的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也对我好一点嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.28,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妈妈说一声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.94,0:06:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的债务怎么都好说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二 有功夫干这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给妈妈买点礼物怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.35,0:06:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.08,0:06:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.35,0:06:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问梓小姐怎么也有债务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.02,0:06:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说她今天把妈妈的波斯地毯弄脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.64,0:06:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为这个 年终奖金没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.42,0:06:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让她写了借据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止 这样的事出了好多次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她快忍不下去了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.53,0:06:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点小礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.07,0:06:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不喜欢听姐姐的话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家人是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 醒醒 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.52,0:06:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.17,0:06:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是一叫就起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面锁着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.07,0:07:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是去看了医生喝了安眠药什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才这么早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会出什么事了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都急出汗来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.02,0:07:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是什么声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.22,0:07:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事情吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生 出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个房间里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.80,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈的房间没有什么奇怪的声音传出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.08,0:07:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 妈妈的房间里有枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.64,0:07:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面锁上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.79,0:07:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有备用钥匙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.92,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个钥匙是特制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有妈妈手上的那一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.45,0:07:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好把门撞开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.25,0:07:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真黑 什么都看不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开关在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.66,0:08:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边墙上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.47,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.97,0:08:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.02,0:08:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是杀人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.82,0:08:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须保护现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.12,0:08:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兰 打电话报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.07,0:08:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被枪杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.90,0:08:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当场死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有搏斗过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直延续到窗边的足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用了那个梯子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这个遗体的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.13,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次都要和你说一样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.22,0:09:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.52,0:09:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛 痛 痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人古川和江
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,64岁 融资公司社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.50,0:09:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在窗外的梯子周围也发现了足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和遗体旁边的足迹一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.17,0:09:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.45,0:09:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人3天前被暴徒袭击过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是同一个犯人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.59,0:09:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有不认识的人从窗户进来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为害怕会朝门的方向逃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.61,0:09:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.64,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你说话的份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 柯南说得对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.26,0:09:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗体倒在窗边说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.98,0:10:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是看见了侵入者之后走到窗边的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.06,0:10:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说被害人可能认识侵入者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.65,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先问问案发时在房子里的人们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.31,0:10:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现遗体时的情况是这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.95,0:10:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川悦子和町田梓两人去2楼叫醒被害人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见房间里传来枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.67,0:10:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利先生和古川浩二撞开门进入室内发现了遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.74,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这为止没有出入吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.52,0:10:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见枪声的时候有什么异样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得当时悦子小姐要去捡掉在地上的手帕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正蹲在地上的时候就听见了枪响
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪响之后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.20,0:10:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.01,0:10:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 警部先生 你们要问到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.13,0:10:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作案的肯定是3天前的那个家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点发通缉什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人已经在通缉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是根据遗体的状况判断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是她认识的人作的案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.39,0:11:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.16,0:11:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上出门之后就没进过妈妈的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.66,0:11:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.74,0:11:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,町田梓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.27,0:11:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.22,0:11:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人对你很不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.13,0:11:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居说今天傍晚你还打翻了红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说一定要报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.15,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓 难道是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是忍无可忍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实这么说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.11,0:12:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.38,0:12:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚我在太太的房间打翻了红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.46,0:12:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是弄湿了的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手表 电视遥控器 地毯等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都仔细擦过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是太太还是说波斯地毯上沾上了污迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.03,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扣除了我今年的年终奖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.33,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还逼我写了借据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.54,0:12:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在忍不住就说了那话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是就像我刚才说的 听见枪声的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.68,0:12:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和悦子小姐在房间外面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.17,0:12:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.13,0:12:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.66,0:12:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你们两人都有不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.46,0:12:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二先生 你当时在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.19,0:12:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 浩二先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.92,0:12:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悦子女士她们两人上了2楼之后 你立即离开了客厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.45,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见枪声后过了半天才回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.63,0:12:57.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.89,0:12:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.61,0:13:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你去哪里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.28,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去给妈妈买点小礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快出去了的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.37,0:13:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听见了枪声就赶紧回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.33,0:13:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说你没有不在场证明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.09,0:13:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.52,0:13:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位再仔细谈谈当时的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从目前的情况来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.95,0:13:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩二先生确实最可疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 有什么地方不大对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.34,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.26,0:13:28.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.93,0:13:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登米先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也来了啊 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来帮名侦探破案吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.85,0:13:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔让我问问这个房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.24,0:13:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有带有计时器的收录机什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.25,0:13:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用计时器就能制造个枪声吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.74,0:13:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 没有这样的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.36,0:13:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视也是老型号的没有计时器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.42,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想的不对吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 登米先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干吧 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那枪声肯定是个机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.23,0:14:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青白色的光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 又说这么难懂的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.96,0:14:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.33,0:14:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪响之前一瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶尔回头看了妈妈的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.02,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间里闪了两下青白色的光然后就突然黑下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.95,0:14:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.82,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青白色光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是登米先生刚才说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 可以这么办的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.26,0:14:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个东西会在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.11,0:14:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.10,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.26,0:14:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和我想的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.67,0:14:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的真多啊 小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.40,0:14:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得有点不对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.08,0:14:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据也全了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人就是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有你说的关键证据啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.69,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了 开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.73,0:15:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.37,0:15:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利老弟 你真的找到犯人了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.81,0:15:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个姿势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.86,0:15:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.84,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把大家都叫到这个房间里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.98,0:15:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.83,0:15:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家都到齐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 目暮警部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据遗体位置来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.09,0:15:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害人认识犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.38,0:15:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们撞开门的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房间里的灯并没有开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.59,0:15:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样被害人是看不清入侵者的脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.81,0:15:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.95,0:15:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.22,0:15:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和江是在被发现之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天还亮着的时候被杀害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.43,0:16:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们听见的枪声呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.46,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪声是犯人为了证明自己不在现场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.75,0:16:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这房间的遥控器拿走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.12,0:16:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外面将电视开关打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.12,0:16:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视节目里正好播放到的枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.34,0:16:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.19,0:16:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样犯人就必须知道枪声播放的准确时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.88,0:16:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.09,0:16:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.97,0:16:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个人知道枪声播放的准确时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.95,0:16:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪声是7:30左右响的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准确时间是7点29分32秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.41,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好是悦子女士公司制作的电视剧里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手枪开枪的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.91,0:16:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 悦子女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:16:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是此次事件的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件的真相很可能是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.78,0:17:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傍晚时悦子女士用梯子从窗户进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和江女士看到她进来就走到窗边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.51,0:17:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就用带有消音器的手枪将和江女士枪杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.46,0:17:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后悦子女士扔掉了作案时穿的衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.47,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟没事人一样出现在我们面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算好时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上她的证人梓小姐上去2楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.77,0:17:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后故意让手帕掉在地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捡手帕的同时 按下了遥控器的开关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.73,0:17:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里说错了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.00,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 浩二说的青白色的光就是电视发出的光线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.95,0:17:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.43,0:17:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开遥控器的时间哪怕只差了一秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会让人听到多余的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.87,0:18:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机关立刻会就被识破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你今天特意戴了电子表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.56,0:18:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 你还弄坏了客厅里面的电视
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2楼的枪声响了的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.31,0:18:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果客厅里的电视里也同样的响起枪声就全完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有证据吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.68,0:18:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.03,0:18:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.85,0:18:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你装作痛哭流涕的样子蹲下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个空子拿出遥控器放在地毯上滑过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.54,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它回到了桌子下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是用的劲有点大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.53,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常就算从桌子掉下来也掉不到那样的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它滑到了桌子脚下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.62,0:18:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个遥控器上还留有你的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.25,0:18:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都进出这个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.79,0:18:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你刚才说早上出去之后还没有进过这个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.09,0:19:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这说的是今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天和前天我就来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.26,0:19:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这房间里把红茶弄洒了的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时电视遥控器是怎么处理的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为上面沾了红茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.43,0:19:19.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仔细地擦干净了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许胡说八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定忘记擦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.01,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.90,0:19:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仔仔细细地擦过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.51,0:19:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去就吵不清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.15,0:19:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登米 请给大家说明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能开始了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.23,0:19:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随时都可以 请吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.33,0:19:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在现场发现的遥控器上发现了两组指纹和掌纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.97,0:19:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是古川悦子的左手第一指到第五指的指纹和掌纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.00,0:20:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一个是町田梓的左手第一指到第五指的指纹和掌纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.21,0:20:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己的指纹还在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.57,0:20:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.57,0:20:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这些吗 登米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.68,0:20:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.79,0:20:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.19,0:20:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 什么行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓小姐并没有忘记擦遥控器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是刚才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指纹还不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.45,0:20:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她如果忘记擦遥控器的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就应该还剩下些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.27,0:20:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在这个房间里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.37,0:20:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直用那个遥控器的古川和江的指纹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.20,0:20:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是她不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.88,0:20:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道我资金周转不灵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.27,0:20:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一分钱都不肯借给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.59,0:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是浩二的赌债她却都替他还了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.15,0:21:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是浩二 浩二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.45,0:21:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚年得子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是宠着浩二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.13,0:21:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是浩二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.88,0:21:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.62,0:21:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古川女士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心情我能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.55,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说能理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.53,0:21:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.90,0:21:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.77,0:21:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了自己的母亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好想想你的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.18,0:23:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 这下应该能看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.32,0:23:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.24,0:23:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高木也是电视迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.43,0:23:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都去租录像带看 很累的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.66,0:23:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.82,0:23:37.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案件啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.43,0:23:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.48,0:23:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那声音是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.58,0:23:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.51,0:24:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.37,0:24:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.67,0:24:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追杀的名侦探（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.95,0:24:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阵雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.54,0:24:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集将在4月10号播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.23,0:24:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一周播出的是剧场版世纪末的魔术师 记得收看哦 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.84,0:00:21.72,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你和我是不同的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.99,0:00:30.73,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜好不同 脚程与表达的方式也大异其趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.49,0:00:37.66,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我们在两人的记忆中正在渐渐褪色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.45,0:00:45.18,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我摸索过 却开始探寻其他人与未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.29,0:00:52.31,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比自己想象的活得更坚强 追寻一种特别的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.43,0:00:56.27,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为难以应付的每一天所苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.57,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ture heart for mystery eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.69,0:01:07.03,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不再迷惑 请别松开你的手腕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.33,0:01:09.99,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是互相伤害的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.09,0:01:21.46,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一直在迷惘的时空中找寻答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.69,0:01:27.90,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}朝着下一个舞台 you take your way
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.48,0:01:32.28,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}请抱紧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.41,0:01:39.41,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,720)}I feel so all in secret life
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.13,0:21:59.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用什么方式表达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.80,0:22:06.44,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能让你明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.54,0:22:15.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从那次以后 不知多少个季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.49,0:22:21.69,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.46,0:22:29.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是笑着守候在我身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.13,0:22:39.48,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不敢告诉我的事情 还有一件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.64,0:22:44.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Secret of my heart 并不是怀疑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.55,0:22:50.62,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管何时 只要还有少许未来的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.72,0:22:55.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相一定会落入手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.73,0:23:02.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法再说什么 只有等到机会
